title: 820-00165 shutsdown near the end of loading OS
message:
Board had corrosion under U3540 and U7870 that got fixed fine, now board turns on, while loading the OS the bar gets to about 80% then disappears a few seconds later image is gone and board stays at around 0.100a for about 10 seconds then board shuts down.

I have tried clean ME BIOS, ultrasonic board  but no luck.

Thanks in advanced for help!

title: 820-00165 shutsdown near the end of loading OS
message: Can you start in safe mode?

title: 820-00165 shutsdown near the end of loading OS
message: Ive tried with 2 different SSD and OS, but I will try safe mode now.

title: 820-00165 shutsdown near the end of loading OS
message: Just tested in safe mode and it boots up but it shut down on the first try.

title: 820-00165 shutsdown near the end of loading OS
message:
So you can get logged in to macOS in safe mode, but turns off in short time?
Or turns off only when you try to access any application?

Try without airport card connected too.
